In [[computer networking]] and [[telecommunications]], a '''broadcast communication network''' is a [[communication network]] which uses [[broadcasting (networks)|broadcasting]] for communication between its [[node (networking)|nodes]]. They take messages from a single sender and transmit to all endpoints on the network.

